    <titleInfo lang="zh">
        <title>從佛教美術看四川地域</title>
    </titleInfo>
    <titleInfo type="translated" lang="en">
        <title>A Look at the Sichuan Region from the Perspective of Buddhist Art</title>
    </titleInfo>
    <titleInfo type="reference">
        <title>Hida 2015a</title>
    </titleInfo>
    
    <abstract>As the title says, this article gives an introduction into the most important Sichuan sites with Buddhist art and excavated artifacts (Han to Song). Xuanzong 玄宗 (r. 712-756) and Xizong 僖宗 (r. 873 to 888) 避難于此地 (Sichuan). Sanxingdui, Han tombs with early Buddha figures, money trees, Grabbeigaben. Roads to Sichuan, history of Sichuan (zu welchen Dynastien gehörte es), Liang dynasty, Wanfo Si , Asoka image, Mao Xian 茂縣 Funde, Blüte der Höhlentempel unter der Tang und Song (die meisten in ganz China), Guangyuan 廣元, Qionglai 邛崍, Chongqing Dazu 重慶大足縣</abstract>
